The canonical agent instructions for this repository live in `AGENTS.md`. Read that file.

Before non-trivial work, also read:

- `docs/CONTEXT.md` — domain glossary (Show, Syntax, Host, Guest, Content, etc.).
- `docs/adr/` — architecture decisions (Drizzle/Postgres, text IDs, unified content model, naming conventions).

If anything in this file appears to contradict `AGENTS.md`, trust `AGENTS.md`.
